3. cs.CV - The paper deals with image-like data (seismic measurements) and proposes a method for feature extraction, which is a common topic in computer vision. 
4. cs.GR - The paper deals with visualization and analysis of geological features, which falls under the scope of computer graphics. 
5. cs.SE - The paper discusses computational cost analysis and validation of the proposed method using numerical examples, which are common topics in software engineering.
